						<h1 id="firstHeading">BitC</h1>			
<div class="dablink">Not to be confused with <a href="http://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Business_in_the_Community" title="Business in the Community">Business in the Community</a>.</div>
<table class="infobox vevent" cellspacing="3" style="border-spacing: 3px; width:22em;">
<caption class="summary" style="">BitC</caption>
<tr class="">
<th scope="row" style="text-align:left;">Designed by</th>
<td class="organiser" style="">Jonathan S. Shapiro, Swaroop Sridhar, and M. Scott Doerrie</td>
</tr>
<tr class="">
<th scope="row" style="text-align:left;"><a href="Software_developer" title="Software developer">Developer</a></th>
<td class="" style="">
<a href="http://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Johns_Hopkins_University" title="Johns Hopkins University">Johns Hopkins University</a>, <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.eros-os.com">The EROS Group, LLC</a>
</td>
</tr>
<tr class="">
<th scope="row" style="text-align:left;"><a href="Software_release_life_cycle" title="Software release life cycle">Stable release</a></th>
<td class="" style="">BitCC 0.9.1 (February 17, 2006)</td>
</tr>
